text: Gerhard Mans (born 4 September 1987) is a Namibian professional racing cyclist. He won the Namibia National Time Trial Championship in 2015. He also rode in two events at the 2014 Commonwealth Games. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Namibian male cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Windhoek Category:Cyclists at the 2014 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for Namibia
